---
// 404 page — standalone Astro page (NOT a content-collection entry).
//
// Was: apps/docs-site/src/content/docs/404.md routed through Starlight's
// content-collection schema. As of Astro 5 + Starlight 0.30 + Zod 4 the
// content schema invocation hits `inst._zod.parse is undefined` because
// Starlight 0.30 expects Zod 3 but the workspace pins Zod 4 via
// @pryzm/schemas. The static-route generation for /404 then fails the
// whole build.
//
// Fix: move the 404 to src/pages/404.astro so it bypasses content
// collections entirely. Astro picks this up as the catch-all 404 for
// Cloudflare Pages + every static host. No content-schema validation;
// the page renders as a plain Astro template.
//
// Track to retire this fix when Starlight 0.30 ships Zod 4 support
// or the workspace de-pins zod 4.
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Page Not Found — PRYZM</title>
    <meta name="description" content="The page you were looking for could not be found." />
    <style>
      :root {
        --pryzm-purple: #6600ff;
        --pryzm-purple-lighter: #8c4dff;
        --pryzm-ink: #0a0a0f;
        --pryzm-paper: #14141c;
        --pryzm-border: #2a2a36;
        --pryzm-text-primary: #f5f5fa;
        --pryzm-text-secondary: #a8a8b5;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0; padding: 0;
        background: var(--pryzm-ink);
        color: var(--pryzm-text-primary);
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--pryzm-purple-lighter);
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      p {
        color: var(--pryzm-text-secondary);
        margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      a.button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background 0.12s, color 0.12s;
      }
      a.button.primary {
        background: var(--pryzm-purple);
        color: #fff;
      }
      a.button.primary:hover,
      a.button.primary:focus-visible {
        background: var(--pryzm-purple-lighter);
      }
      a.button.secondary {
        background: var(--pryzm-paper);
        color: var(--pryzm-text-primary);
        border: 1px solid var(--pryzm-border);
      }
      a.button.secondary:hover,
      a.button.secondary:focus-visible {
        border-color: var(--pryzm-purple-lighter);
        color: var(--pryzm-purple-lighter);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="code">404</div>
      <h1>Page not found</h1>
      <p>The page you were looking for doesn't exist on pryzm.so. Try the home page, or one of the canonical surfaces below.</p>
      <div class="links">
        <a class="button primary" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/manifesto">Manifesto</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/trust">Trust</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
